msgctxt "180_Saito"
msgid "You're not the first who's tried to fly the coop. But guess what? Not a single soul has made it out."
msgstr "You're not the first who's tried to fly the coop. But guess what? Not a single soul has made it out."

msgctxt "192_Saito"
msgid "Know why that is? 'Cause I've clipped their wings the moment they were dumb enough to try."
msgstr "Know why that is? 'Cause I've clipped their wings the moment they were dumb enough to try."

msgctxt "204_Saito"
msgid "But go ahead, let's see how far you get. You're still nowhere close."
msgstr "But go ahead, let's see how far you get. You're still nowhere close."

msgctxt "240_Saejima"
msgid "(Hamazaki just said to keep the guards busy, but it's easier to just flatten 'em all instead. Least I'll get the key quicker that way.)"
msgstr "(Hamazaki just said to keep the guards busy, but it's easier to just flatten 'em all instead. Least I'll get the key quicker that way.)"

